{"tid":2075361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【關家姐】張宇人質疑許智峯撐環保但無手帕  許智峯揮動手帕","createTime":"2020-06-22T20:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T01:08:47.000Z","uid":86509,"like":148,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd2c0fa8181503e30ce1a57a3a8a7e29ff0bbad","tid":2075361,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T20:48:21.000Z","msg":"【張宇人質疑民主派撐環保但無手帕　問許智峯有無】<br />\n【許智峯揮動手帕　張宇人： 你都算環保啲】<br />\n<br />\n立法會審議有關垃圾徵費修訂條例草案的委員會，通過終止審議工作。<br />\n<br />\n討論期間，飲食界立法會議員張宇人質疑民主派議員，口口聲聲說支持環保，卻連手帕也沒攜帶。他問立法會議員許智峯，有沒攜帶手帕時，許智峯隨即舉起自己的手帕。張宇人回應：「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你都算環保啲</strong></span></span>」。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #RTHK #張宇人 #許智峯 #手帕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2602872203316490/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F2602872203316490%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7vSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=2e4c987c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/2602872203316490/</a>"},{"pid":"8f899f2596a49e2cb7bda691afed096e4a339624","tid":2075361,"uid":86509,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T20:49:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你都算環保啲。。。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/